4214 - Local Trucking With Storage Summary > KERRY LOGISTICS COLD CHAIN (AUSTRALIA) PTY. LTD. is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover local trucking with storage. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. KERRY LOGISTICS COLD CHAIN (AUSTRALIA) PTY. LTD. is headquartered in Laverton North, Victoria. It is headed by executive director Ian Charles Trimboli. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $34.34 million. Its net profit totalled $2.67 million. KERRY LOGISTICS COLD CHAIN (AUSTRALIA) PTY. LTD. forms part of the transportation, communications, electric, gas, and sanitary services industry sector.
